  > EOF

.. And another client:

  $ cd ..

  $ hg clone server other-client
  updating to branch default
  1 files updated, 0 files merged, 0 files removed, 0 files unresolved

  $ cd client

We can now share these draft changesets:

  $ hg push ../non-publishing-server -r tools
